{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoRepeatUntil\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">expandDoRepeatUntil</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Macro\">Macro</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoRepeatUntil","kind":"def","line":43,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoRepeatUntil","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.lean#L43-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoWhile\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">expandDoWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Macro\">Macro</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoWhile","kind":"def","line":39,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.expandDoWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.lean#L39-L41"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoRepeat\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabDoRepeat</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElab\">DoElab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Builtin do-element elaborator for `repeat` (syntax kind `Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeat`).\n\nExpands to `for _ in Loop.mk do ...`. When the body cannot `break`, the loop's own expression\ntype is fixed to `PUnit`, yet the surrounding do block may require a different result type;\nwe append an `unreachable!` so the continuation has a polymorphic value of any type. The\n`unreachable!` is never actually executed (the loop never terminates normally), and any\ndead-code warning that fires on the surrounding continuation is actionable — the user can\nremove the following code without breaking the do block's type.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.html#Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoRepeat","kind":"def","line":19,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoRepeat","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Repeat.lean#L19-L37"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.BuiltinDo.Basic","Lean.Elab.BuiltinDo.For","Lean.Parser.Do"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.BuiltinDo.Repeat"}